"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"4, Garden of Eden｜伊甸园\\n\\nI opened the exit of the holographic cocoon room with my consciousness and slid out of it. Stepping on the soft sand with both feet, feeling the slight sea breeze blowing, every pore in the body expands comfortably. I stepped on the rise and fall of the sea and walked freely along the coastline. The holographic cocoon room was also rolling freely, suddenly behind me, and suddenly ran in front of me, but always kept within a proper distance from me.With the weak me and the inseparable holographic cocoon room, I suddenly remembered an ancient animal, a snail, that I had seen in a book, and couldn't help but smile. The sea water reflected my well-proportioned figure, flowing hair, and that beautiful face.\\n\\n我用意识打开了全息茧房的出口，从里面滑了出去。两只脚丫踩在柔软的沙粒上，感受着令人微醺的海风吹拂，全身的每一个毛孔都舒服地扩张开来。我踩着海水的涨落，沿着海岸线自由自在地走着。全息茧房也自由自在的滚动着，忽而在我的身后，忽而跑到我的前面去了，但始终和我保持在一个适当的距离范围之内。柔弱的我，加上不离不弃的全息茧房，我忽然想起来曾经在书上看到过的一种古代动物，蜗牛，不由得“扑哧”笑了一下。海水倒映出我匀称的身材、飘逸的长发，还有那姣好的面庞。\\n\\nOf course, every woman in the White World has a nearly perfect appearance and physique. More importantly, we all have super high IQs. Through the brain-computer chip, we can communicate with the holographic cocoon room at a long distance, and instantly retrieve and obtain all the information and data that the entire mankind has mastered since history.\\n\\n \\n 当然，白世界里的每一位女性都有着近乎完美的外貌和体格。更为重要的是，我们都有着超高的智商。通过脑机芯片，我们可以远距离和全息茧房通信，瞬间检索并获取整个人类自有史以来所掌握的全部信息和资料。\\n\\nAll machines and robots run in the white world, and they are the material basis of all meta-universes. They run automatically most of the time, are managed by AI, and rarely require maintenance. If we need to intervene in operation, maintenance and management, it will not be to operate the machine directly in the white world, but to log in to a certain meta-universe to operate and repair the digital twin of the machine in the meta-universe. Our operations in the meta universe will be transformed into robot work instructions, and then the robot will physically operate and overhaul the machine in the white world.\\n\\n白世界里运行着全部的机器和机器人，它们是所有元宇宙的物质基础。它们绝大部分时间都是自动运行的，由AI负责管理，很少需要维护。如果需要我们介入运维和管理，也不会是直接在白世界中去操作机器，而是要先登陆到某个元宇宙里面去，在元宇宙里操作和检修机器的数字孪生体。我们在元宇宙中的操作，会被转化为机器人的工作指令，然后由机器人在白世界中对机器进行物理的操作和检修。\\n\\nAmong all these machines, the most important one is the Bitcoin system that has been in operation since some time in ancient times. This system is the ledger of the entire white world, the ultimate value anchor of all meta-universes, and a timer.\\n\\n在这所有的机器中，最重要的一个就是自古代某个时候开始运行至今的比特币系统。这套系统是整个白世界的账本，所有元宇宙的最终价值锚点，以及计时器。\\n\\nSince artificial lighting has replaced the sun in the White World, we have long abandoned the concept of \\\"rise at sunrise and rest at sunset\\\" and instead adopt the block counting of the Bitcoin system for timing. At the same time, since each meta-universe we build has different time-space settings, how do we know the correspondence of time when we are in different meta-universes? The block time of Bitcoin can only be used as the standard time consensus between different meta-universes. For example, in \\\"Plato\\\", the time setting is 2140 AD; and when I landed in \\\"Galileo\\\", the time setting went tens of thousands of years later. Then when I shuttle between them, I have to pay attention to the block time of Bitcoin, just like I did when I logged out of \\\"Plato\\\", in order to align the history and memory in different meta-universes.\\n\\n由于白世界里人工照明取代了太阳，我们早已抛弃了“日出而起、日落而息”的概念，转而采用比特币系统的区块计数来计时。同时，由于我们所建立的各个元宇宙都有不同的时空设定，那么如何在置身于不同元宇宙的时候，知晓时间的对应关系呢？只能靠比特币的区块时间来作为不同元宇宙之间的标准时间共识。比如，在“柏拉图”中，时间设定是公元纪年2140年；而当我登陆到“伽利略”去的时候，时间设定就跑到了几万年之后去了。那么当我穿梭其间的时候，我就要留意比特币的区块时间，就像我在登出“柏拉图”的时候所做的那样，以此对齐不同元宇宙中的历史和记忆。\\n\\nIf the local time numbers in the two meta-universes are the order of priority, then I met Su Lin in \\\"Galileo\\\" after tens of thousands of years after forming a sambo relationship with Nana in \\\"Plato\\\". Only by taking the Bitcoin block time as a reference standard, I can clearly know that Su Lin's sudden disappearance was far before I met Nana.\\n\\n如果以两个元宇宙中的本地时间数字大小为先后顺序，那么我在“伽利略”里认识苏琳，是在“柏拉图”中和娜娜结为sambo关系的几万年之后了。只有以比特币区块时间为参考标准，我才能够清晰的知道，苏琳的忽然消失，是远早于我和娜娜相识的。 \\n \\n\\nThe time in the meta-universe is diverse, variable, and relative, while the block time of Bitcoin is unitary, unchanging, and absolute. Similarly, various currency systems will be set up in different meta-universes, but in any case, Bitcoin is the basic currency that prevails in all meta-universes. Moreover, it is unified, unique, and non-superior in any meta-universe. All other currencies or tokens confined to a certain meta-universe, like colorful balloons, will eventually be tied to the electronic gold of Bitcoin. Otherwise, it will fly into the hyperinflationary sky like a broken balloon.\\n\\n元宇宙中的时间是多元的、可变的、相对的，而比特币的区块时间是一元的、不变的、绝对的。同样的，在不同元宇宙中都会设定自己五花八门的货币体系，但是无论如何，比特币是在所有元宇宙中通行的基础货币。并且，在任何一个元宇宙中都是统一的、唯一的、不可超发的。所有其他局限于某个元宇宙中的货币或者代币，就像五颜六色的气球，最终都要拴在比特币这块电子黄金上。否则，就会像断了线的气球，飞向恶性通胀的天空。\\n\\nIn a sense, the white world and all meta-universes supported by the white world are based on Bitcoin. The Bitcoin standard is the new \\\"Bretton Woods System\\\" of all the world. Unlike the depictions in some ancient science fiction movies, we humans have become ignorant human batteries, our bodies live in the dirty real world, our souls are placed in virtual space and time, but we don't know our own situation. We know that Gödel has long proved that this kind of system that deceives everyone is impossible and complete, and it must have its loopholes.\\n\\n某种意义上，白世界以及由白世界所支撑的全部元宇宙，都是以比特币为本位的。比特币本位，就是所有世界的新“布雷顿森林体系”。不像古代某些科幻电影里面描绘的，我们人类变成了愚昧的人肉电池，肉身活在肮脏的现实世界，灵魂安放在虚拟时空，却不知道自己的处境。我们知道，哥德尔早就证明了这种蒙蔽所有人的系统是不可能的完备的，必有其漏洞。\\n\\nEach of us is very aware of the White World and all meta-universes, and knows everything. With the assistance of the holographic cocoon room, everyone has all human knowledge. Everyone is the whole mankind, and the whole mankind is everybody. Just like Bitcoin's ledger, it is fully replicated on every full node. One hundred percent redundancy determines that it is difficult for humans to be completely wiped out. Even if I am the only one left, as long as I want to, I can master all the knowledge needed to manipulate and rebuild all machines, and I can multiply the entire human race on my own. Just like what the Nuwa Empress did in the legend of a certain oriental nation in ancient times.\\n\\n我们每一个人都十分清楚白世界和所有的元宇宙，知晓一切。在全息茧房的辅助下，每个人都拥有全部的人类知识。每一个人都是整个人类，整个人类就是每一个人。就像比特币的账本，在每一个全节点上都完整复制。百分之百的冗余度决定了，人类很难被彻底消灭。即使只剩下了我一个人，只要我愿意，我可以掌握操控和再造所有机器所需的全部知识，并且可以以一己之力，繁衍整个人类族群。就像上古时代某个东方民族传说中的女娲娘娘所做到的那样。\\n\\nThe memories of the avatars in the various meta-universes are not connected. Only by relying on our memory in the white world, we synchronize the data of the avatar in the meta universe when we log in to the meta universe, and then synchronize to another avatar when we log in to another meta universe. The White World acts as a \\\"data bus\\\" connecting all meta-universes.\\n\\n各个元宇宙中的化身，记忆并不相通。只有靠白世界的我们的记忆，在登入元宇宙时同步该元宇宙中化身的数据，待到登入另一个元宇宙时再同步给另外一个化身。白世界充当了连接所有元宇宙之间的“数据总线”。\\n\\nWe humans have never been so close to \\\"God\\\" as we are today. We humans have finally reached what the philosopher and biologist De Nijin calls the \\\"Point Omega\\\" . Our mental layer has achieved the last leap in the evolution of the universe, breaking through the relationship between matter and spirit, sublating matter, and entering the \\\"super-person\\\", \\\"super-national\\\", \\\"super-race\\\", \\\"super-conscious\\\" and \\\"super-time\\\". The state of complete spiritualization is the most complete sacred state that people have long desired for a long time.\\n\\n我们人类，从来没有像今天这样如此接近“神”。我们人类，终于抵达了哲学家和生物学家德日进所说的“欧米伽点”（Point Omega）。我们的心智层实现了宇宙进化最后一次飞跃，突破了物质与精神的关系，扬弃物质，进入到了“超个人”、“超国家”、“超种族”、“超意识”和“超时空”的完全精神化境界，即人们长期以来所渴望的最完满的神圣境界。\\n\\nContrary to what many people think, I don't like the colorful world and the colorful life in the meta universe so much. On the contrary, I often \\\"lazy\\\" to host the avatar in the metaverse to the AI, and then I log out of the metaverse and return to the white world. Because I think that the white world is the most dull and most real world. Every time you are in it, the whole body, soul, and soul will get a kind of \\\"philosophical serenity\\\". Only in the white world, I can enjoy a different kind of loneliness alone, facing the sea, and spring flowers blooming.There are many people who like the White World just like me. We all feel that the White World is our true \\\"Garden of Eden\\\".\\n\\n和很多人想象的不一样，我并不是那么地喜欢元宇宙里七彩斑斓的世界和缤纷无限的生活。相反的，我常常“偷懒”把元宇宙中的化身托管给AI，自己则登出元宇宙，回到白世界。因为我觉得，白世界才是那个最平淡而又最真实的世界，每每身处其中，整个身心灵就会获得一种“哲学的宁静”（philosophical serenity）。只有在白世界中，我可以独自一个人享受别样的孤独，面向大海，春暖花开。和我一样喜欢白世界的人很多，我们都觉得，白世界才是我们真正的“伊甸园”。\\n\\nI lifted my head gently, looked at the white sails in the distance, listened to the screams of sea gulls on the sea, stroked my soft long hair, called a cup of Mojito through the holographic cocoon room, and a copy of Plato’s copy of the ancient Greek philosopher Plato. Book. In a short while, the robot delivered the Mojito and \\\"Dreamland\\\" I wanted, and also delivered a reclining chair and a small bar next to the chair. I read the book comfortably and fell asleep unconsciously. In my sleep, I seemed to dream of Su Lin and the exciting and happy time with her during the interstellar adventure in Galileo.\\n\\n \\n 我轻轻地扬起头，看着远处的点点白帆，听着海面上海鸥的鸣叫，抚弄了一下柔顺的长发，通过全息茧房呼叫了一杯Mojito，以及一本古希腊哲学家柏拉图的书。不一会儿，机器人就送来了我要的Mojito和《理想国》，还贴心地递送上了一把躺椅和椅边的小吧台。我惬意地读起了书，不知不觉地睡着了。在睡梦中，我仿佛梦到了苏琳，以及和她结伴在“伽利略”中星际探险时刺激而开心的美好时光。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/qzDlBE1tu6g_RGDVGcg0J.jpg?height=900&width=1920)\\n\\n \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n  \\n \",\"timestamp\":1639139433,\"title\":\"Good morning, Nana｜早安，娜娜——Chapter Four｜第四章\"},\"digest\":\"EyJYsXE6QEjSyYiue4L9m3Jx0hdpLEc0KGKX4lrUK9Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x43B004D591808B79cAe88F29C32Fff781Aee0e11\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"J0K6WSYCAiNsDyfYKfNQUBwz5Y2DHM1lClyZHsES8J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"T756lTat5fLMyTAcCBeRUgArjhma_41p1QdFqw3bY4E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"_srpirPaRZzAAjRYe9FbPQfjGX2JfGC1ePva-P6vn9whou2rThikYNp9lvxerdfvjWjhFFbxZMubLuDglw1AFA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4499ae3483ae8a062ad6bae21a5f5564218c00d5d5f042da8178ab89b45bad5221946568fb243bbb56120558dea32ce17d5fc49e7f8609949a27d439840d69591b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"J0K6WSYCAiNsDyfYKfNQUBwz5Y2DHM1lClyZHsES8J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"T756lTat5fLMyTAcCBeRUgArjhma_41p1QdFqw3bY4E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"EyJYsXE6QEjSyYiue4L9m3Jx0hdpLEc0KGKX4lrUK9Y\"}"